  Ti7 Sin5-keh hit pun2 chheh e5 lai7-bin7 u7 kong2: ¡§Koan-he7 sin5 e5 seng3-chit, u7 chit8 e5 te7-it ho2 e5 be7-thang cheng3-beng5, tui3 chhong3-cho7 te7 kap te7-chiuN7 e5 lang5 e5 su7-chek tiong be7-thang chhoe7 chhut¡¨ In kong2 Sin5 chiau3 ka-ki7 e5 heng5-chong7 cho7 lang5, sou2-i2 Sin5 kap lang5 oan5-choan5 chit8-iuN7. In koh kong2 u7 lang5 na7 ai3 chai-iaN2 Sin5 si7 sim2-mih8 khoan2 chiu7 tioh8 khoaN3 lang5 e5 heng5-siong7 sim2-mih8 khoan2 chiu7 thang chai, in-ui7 lang5 si7 chiau3 I e5 heng5-siong7 cho7 e5.¡¨ 
